* text=auto

### These files are text and should be normalized (convert crlf => lf)
*.cs      text diff=csharp
*.xaml    text
*.csproj  text
*.sln     text
*.tt      text
*.ps1     text
*.cmd     text
*.msbuild text
*.md      text

### These files are binary
*.jpg binary
*.png binary
*.gif binary

### Sitecore/TDS specific settings
*.item -text ### TDS files should be treated as binary
